snippet.title: LOST IN FAILURES (ANNOUNCEMENT TEASER)
snippet.description:
This is LOST IN FAILURES, a new survival, adventure and action game set in a parallel dimension where humans never existed! Your objective as a player is to explore, collect resources, create items and evolve to try to get back to the reality in which you lived before. Our team is working hard to create an immersive, innovative, realistic, mysterious and challenging experience! The game's release date is being planned for the first half of 2022. We are very happy with the result so far! We will soon share more information about the product, Stay tuned!

Our Website: https://www.lightstationdeveloper.com/

Social Medias:
